source: TEXT_HEAVNZ635_01903_SEQ_00<tab>Fabrellet seems awfully satisfied with himself.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ635_01903_SEQ_00<tab>キャンプ・クラウドトップのファブルレーは、何かを思いついたようだ。

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ635_01903_SEQ_01<tab>Fabrellet recently discovered several gastornis nests east of the Rosehouse, and was struck with an incredible idea. All he requires to set his plan into motion is a single egg. Make your way east of the Rosehouse, and retrieve an egg from one of the gastornis nests.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ635_01903_SEQ_01<tab>ファブルレーから<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8AFA01 /var>を取ってくるよう頼まれた。アバラシア雲海のウィセントヘッドにある「<var 28 ((EObj)) F61E9B1301 /var>」を調べ、「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8AFA01 /var>」を入手しよう。

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ635_01903_SEQ_02<tab>You have obtained a gastornis egg. Return to Camp Cloudtop and deliver it to Fabrellet.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ635_01903_SEQ_02<tab><var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8AFA01 /var>を入手した。キャンプ・クラウドトップの「ファブルレー」に「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8AFA01 /var>」を渡そう。

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ635_01903_SEQ_03<tab>You deliver a still-warm egg to Fabrellet who is now giddy with excitement. It seemed as though he intended to make the egg his next meal, but in truth, his plan is to raise a bird of his own for an ever-ready supply of eggs.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ635_01903_SEQ_03<tab>ファブルレーに<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8AFA01 /var>を渡した。彼はこの卵を孵して育て、産ませた卵を取るつもりのようだ。

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ635_01903_TODO_00<tab>Obtain an egg from a gastornis nest.

target: TEXT_HEAVNZ635_01903_TODO_01<tab>ファブルレーに<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8AFA01 /var>を渡す

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ635_01903_FABRELLET_000_000<tab>I've had great ideas in my day, but I must say I've truly outdone myself this time. No doubt you're curious to know what I'm planning.
target:
TEXT_HEAVNZ635_01903_FABRELLET_000_000これは……いいこと思いついてしまったぞ！
「ウィセントヘッド」で、ガストルニスの巣を見つけたんだ。

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ635_01903_FABRELLET_000_001<tab>Well, not long ago I discovered a scattering of gastornis nests east of the Rosehouse. If you could retrieve a single egg from the nest for me, all will be made clear.
target:
TEXT_HEAVNZ635_01903_FABRELLET_000_001巣の中に卵があれば、もうけものだ！
巣を調べて、「」をひとつ、
取ってきてくれないか？

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ635_01903_FABRELLET_000_010<tab>For my plan to work, all I need is a single egg from the nest. Once you reach the Rosehouse, it's not very far.
target:
TEXT_HEAVNZ635_01903_FABRELLET_000_010巣の中に卵があれば、もうけものだ！
巣を調べて、「」をひとつ、
取ってきてくれないか？

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ635_01903_SYSTEM_000_015<tab>You search the gastornis nest, but find nothing...
TEXT_HEAVNZ635_01903_FABRELLET_000_020<tab>Were you able to procure an egg from one of the nests?
target:
TEXT_HEAVNZ635_01903_FABRELLET_000_020巣の中に卵があれば、もうけものだ！
巣を調べて、「」をひとつ、
取ってきてくれないか？

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ635_01903_FABRELLET_000_021<tab>Oh, it's still warm! Excellent! Eggs will make an excellent addition to our stock of provisions.
target:
TEXT_HEAVNZ635_01903_FABRELLET_000_021おお！　まだあったかいな！
ありがとうよ！

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ635_01903_FABRELLET_000_022<tab>Hm? Don't be silly. A single egg cannot feed the entire camp. But when I've hatched and raised a gastornis of my own, we shall have all the eggs we could ever ask for!
target:
TEXT_HEAVNZ635_01903_FABRELLET_000_022……え？　いやいや、食べるんじゃない。
この卵を孵して、育ててやるのさ。
そうすりゃ将来は、毎日卵が食べられるだろ？
